Package: gramps
Version: 0.9.5
Revision: 1
Source: mirror:sourceforge:%n/%n-%v.tar.gz  
Source-MD5: 2f00c26180fbcf1973ea477d538a57e4
BuildDepends: gnome-core-dev (>= 1.2.0-1), imlib, orbit-dev, esound, popt, gettext-dev, gettext-bin, scrollkeeper
Depends: python23 | python23-nox, gnome-python-py23, pygtk-py23, imlib-shlibs, reportlab-py23, pil-py23
ConfigureParams: --libdir='%p/lib'  --bindir='%p/bin' --mandir=%p/share/man
PatchScript: sed 's|@PREFIX@|%p|g' <%a/%n.patch | patch -p1
CompileScript: <<
export PYTHON='%p/bin/python2.3'; ./configure %c
make clean
make
<<
InstallScript: make install DESTDIR=%d
PostInstScript: scrollkeeper-rebuilddb
License: GPL
DocFiles: NEWS README AUTHORS ChangeLog COPYING TODO
Description: Genealogy software for GNOME/GTK
DescDetail: <<
Current Features
* GEDCOM import and export
* Merge capability
* Display filters
* Web page generation using a built-in template or a user defined template
* Unlimited bookmarks
* Soundex generator
* Relationship calculator
Uses reportlab and pil for generating reports.
<<
